00 p-3\"><p class=\"font-semibold\">Job Board Analytics</p><p class=\"text-gray-500 mt-1\">v1.0.0</p></div></div></aside><div class=\"flex-1 flex flex-col overflow-hidden\"><main class=\"flex-1 overflow-y-auto\"><section class=\"max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16 sm:py-24\"><div class=\"text-center mb-16\"><h2 class=\"text-5xl sm:text-6xl font-bold text-white mb-6\">Take The Reins</h2><p class=\"text-xl sm:text-2xl text-slate-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto\">Facilitate your own pathway forward—unemployed or career-changing, you&#x27;re in control.</p></div><div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-16\"><div class=\"bg-slate-800/50 border border-slate-700 rounded-xl p-8 hover:bg-slate-800/70 transition\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 bg-indigo-600/20 rounded-lg mb-6\"><svg class=\"w-6 h-6 text-indigo-400\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3\">Create a Framework for Your Idea</h3><p class=\"text-slate-400\">Define your vision, identify your goals, and map out the steps to get there. Build on ideas that matter to you.</p></div><div class=\"bg-slate-800/50 border border-slate-700 rounded-xl p-8 hover:bg-slate-800/70 transition\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 bg-emerald-600/20 rounded-lg mb-6\"><svg class=\"w-6 h-6 text-emerald-400\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M12 4.354a4 4 0 110 5.292M15 10H9m6 0a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3\">Collaborate on the Approach</h3><p class=\"text-slate-400\">Connect with mentors, peers, and experts. Get feedback, share ideas, and learn from the community.</p></div><div class=\"bg-slate-800/50 border border-slate-700 rounded-xl p-8 hover:bg-slate-800/70 transition\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 bg-rose-600/20 rounded-lg mb-6\"><svg class=\"w-6 h-6 text-rose-400\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M12 6.253v13m0-13C6.5 6.253 2 10.998 2 17.25c0 5.079 3.855 9.26 8.756 9.589M12 6.253c5.5 0 10 4.745 10 10.997 0 5.079-3.855 9.26-8.756 9.589m0 0A8.991 8.991 0 0121 12a8.991 8.991 0 01-8.756 8.589\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3\">Build Your Manifesto</h3><p class=\"text-slate-400\">Speak in your own way about you, not a resume. Give mind bending examples of who you are, what you have done and your aim for this new phase ahead.</p></div></div><div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-5 gap-6 mb-16\"><a class=\"bg-slate-700 hover:bg-slate-600 text-white font-semibold px-8 py-4 rounded-lg transition text-center\" href=\"/hub/recent\">Your Recent Manifestos</a><a class=\"bg-indigo-600 hover:bg-indigo-700 text-white font-semibold px-8 py-4 rounded-lg transition text-center\" href=\"/hub/projects/new\">Create a Project</a><a class=\"bg-emerald-600 hover:bg-emerald-700 text-white font-semibold px-8 py-4 rounded-lg transition text-center\" href=\"/hub/projects\">Collaborate</a><a class=\"bg-rose-600 hover:bg-rose-700 text-white font-semibold px-8 py-4 rounded-lg transition text-center\" href=\"/hub/members/new\">Build Your Manifesto</a><a class=\"bg-orange-600 hover:bg-orange-700 text-white font-semibold px-8 py-4 rounded-lg transition text-center\" href=\"/marketing/launcher\">📧 Launch Campaign</a></div><div class=\"bg-slate-800/30 border border-slate-700 rounded-xl p-8 sm:p-12\"><h3 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6\">How TakeTheReins Works</h3><div class=\"space-y-4 text-slate-300\"><p><strong>For Job Seekers:</strong> Whether you&#x27;re unemployed or career-changing, use TakeTheReins to take control of your pathway. Find opportunities aligned with your skills, connect with mentors, ask questions, and build a manifesto that represents who you are.</p><p><strong>For Mentors:</strong> Share your expertise, guide others, and build impact in a community focused on real growth and collaboration.</p><p><strong>For Employers:</strong> Connect with pre-vetted, passionate talent. Post jobs, discover candidates, and hire people ready to make an impact.</p></div></div></section><footer class=\"bg-slate-900/50 border-t border-slate-700 mt-24\"><div class=\"max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-8 text-center text-slate-500 text-sm\"><p>Take The Reins © 2026 • Empowering your own pathway forward</p></div></footer></main></div></div></div><script id=\"__NEXT_DATA__\" type=\"application/json\">{\"props\":{\"pageProps\":{}},\"page\":\"/hub\",\"query\":{},\"buildId\":\"A8ZS1-JPDIjUeTFM33ndo\",\"nextExport\":true,\"autoExport\":true,\"isFallback\":false,\"scriptLoader\":[]}</script></body></html>","isFullyStaticPage":true}